author: acumiskey
msg: All AFP library classes without Renderer dependencies moved from org.apache.fop.renderer.afp.* to org.apache.fop.afp.*.
AbstractNamedAFPObject now truncates names to the last x characters of the name string instead of the first x (where x is the name length of the structured field).

author: cziegeler
msg: SLING-339 Implementing a job acknowledge mechanism: All started jobs are queried after a configured time, if someone started to process them. If not, they're requeued. If more than one job processor wants to process a job, only the first one is used to notify the job event handler of success/failure.
